https://digitalpedagogy.mla.hcommons.org/keywords/disability/ and
https://digitalpedagogy.mla.hcommons.org/keywords/digital-divides/

(Remember to check out the curated artifacts in those pieces)

Read about universal design in education:
https://www.washington.edu/doit/programs/center-universal-design-education/overview
http://www.cast.org/our-work/about-udl.html

